Natuwa ba ako sa kanya?

48
00:02:46.291 --> 00:02:47.893
May proof ka ba?

49
00:02:47.917 --> 00:02:49.186
Dahil ginagawa ko!

50
00:02:49.210 --> 00:02:52.064
May patunay ako na pinatay mo si Choi Hae-sik!

51
00:02:52.088 --> 00:02:54.942
