Hindi ba si Sam-sik yun?

164
00:08:33.387 --> 00:08:36.408
- Sam-sik! Kabutihan!
- Sam-sik!

165
00:08:36.432 --> 00:08:37.743
Goodness, Sam-sik!

166
00:08:37.767 --> 00:08:40.162
Anong gagawin natin? May sunog!

167
00:08:40.186 --> 00:08:41.830
Tumawag sa 119!

168
00:08:41.854 --> 00:08:43.457
- Tama, 119!
- Kabutihan, Sam-sik.

169
00:08:43.481 --> 00:08:44.829
- Tumawag sa 119.
- Kabutihan, Sam-sik.

170
00:08:44.853 --> 00:08:46.251
